text: Didi No. 1 () is a Bengali television game show for women, launched in 2010. The show telecast on Zee Bangla six days a week and also available on ZEE5 digitally. == Seasons == * Season 1: Host: Pushpita Mukherjee * Season 2: Host: Rachna Banerjee * Season 3:Host: June Malia * Season 4: Host: Rachna Banerjee * Season 5: Host: Debashree Roy * Season 6: Host: Rachna Banerjee * Season 7: Host: Rachna Banerjee * Season 8: Host: Rachna Banerjee / Sudipa Chatterjee and Sourav Das (for one week) * Season 9: Host: Rachna Banerjee == References == == Other websites == * Didi No. 1 at ZEE5 * Category:Reality television series
